### US1 — List all books
GET http://localhost:8080/books
Accept: application/json


### US2 — Create a book
POST http://localhost:8080/books
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "isbn": "9780134685991",
  "title": "Effective Java",
  "author": "Joshua Bloch",
  "price": 45.0,
  "image": "https://example.com/book.jpg"
}


### US2 — Create duplicate book (Conflict)
POST http://localhost:8080/books
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "isbn": "9780134685991",
  "title": "Duplicate Book",
  "author": "Someone",
  "price": 10,
  "image": "https://example.com/test.jpg"
}


### US3 — Get book by ISBN (English)
GET http://localhost:8080/books/9780134685991
Accept-Language: en


### US3 — Get book by ISBN (Portuguese)
GET http://localhost:8080/books/9780134685991
Accept-Language: pt


### US3 — Get non-existing book
GET http://localhost:8080/books/999999


### US4 — Replace book (PUT)
PUT http://localhost:8080/books/9780134685991
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Effective Java 4th Edition",
  "author": "Joshua Bloch",
  "price": 50,
  "image": "https://example.com/book-new.jpg"
}


### US5 — Patch book
PATCH http://localhost:8080/books/9780134685991
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "price": 55
}


### US6 — Delete book
DELETE http://localhost:8080/books/9780134685991


### US6 — Delete non-existing book
DELETE http://localhost:8080/books/111111


### Create book again (for review tests)
POST http://localhost:8080/books
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "isbn": "9781491950357",
  "title": "Designing Data Intensive Applications",
  "author": "Martin Kleppmann",
  "price": 60,
  "image": "https://example.com/ddia.jpg"
}


### US7 — List reviews for a book
GET http://localhost:8080/books/9781491950357/reviews


### US8 — Create review
POST http://localhost:8080/books/9781491950357/reviews
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "rating": 5,
  "comment": "Excellent book about distributed systems."
}


### US8 — Create review with validation error
POST http://localhost:8080/books/9781491950357/reviews
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "rating": 10,
  "comment": "Invalid rating"
}


### US9 — Replace review
PUT http://localhost:8080/books/9781491950357/reviews/1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "rating": 4,
  "comment": "Updated review comment."
}


### US10 — Patch review
PATCH http://localhost:8080/books/9781491950357/reviews/1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "rating": 3
}


### US11 — Delete review
DELETE http://localhost:8080/books/9781491950357/reviews/1


### US11 — Delete non-existing review
DELETE http://localhost:8080/books/9781491950357/reviews/99